>", "isCorrect": false, "image": null}], "correctValue": null, "solution": {"text": "<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://cdn-question-pool.getmarks.app/pyq/jee_main/1ca50b91-8500-4d58-9b8f-0b4574c42e7d-874e8a3a-71d6-405c-8d39-79d277f30430-9894462.PNG\" style=\"width: 300px; height: 139px;\" /></p><p>Let the charge&nbsp;<math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mn>40</mn><mo>&#160;</mo><mi>&#956;C</mi></math>&nbsp;be placed at a distance&nbsp;<math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><msub><mi>X</mi><mn>0</mn></msub></math>&nbsp;from the origin&nbsp;as shown in the figure.</p><p>For the electric field at&nbsp;<math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>x</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>2</mn></math>&nbsp;to be <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mn>0</mn></math>,</p><p><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><msub><mi>E</mi><mi>P</mi></msub><mo>=</mo><mn>0</mn><mspace linebreak=\"newline\"/><mo>&#8658;</mo><mfrac><mrow><mi>k</mi><mo>&#215;</mo><mn>10</mn></mrow><msup><mn>2</mn><mn>2</mn></msup></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mi>k</mi><mo>&#215;</mo><mn>40</mn><mo>&#160;</mo></mrow><msup><mfenced><mrow><msub><mi>X</mi><mn>0</mn></msub><mo>-</mo><mn>2</mn></mrow></mfenced><mn>2</mn></msup></mfrac></math></p><p><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mo>&#8658;</mo><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mn>2</mn></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mn>2</mn><mrow><msub><mi>X</mi><mn>0</mn></msub><mo>-</mo><mn>2</mn></mrow></mfrac></math></p><p><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mo>&#8658;</mo><msub><mi>X</mi><mn>0</mn></msub><mo>-</mo><mn>2</mn><mo>=</mo><mn>4</mn></math></p><p>Therefore, the charge is located at&nbsp;<math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><msub><mi>X</mi><mn>0</mn></msub><mo>=</mo><mn>4</mn><mo>+</mo><mn>2</mn><mo>=</mo><mn>6</mn><mo>&#160;</mo><mi>cm</mi></math></p>", "image": null}, "videoSolution": null, "numericalUpperLimit": null, "numericalLowerLimit": null, "questionLabels": [], "__v": 0, "masterId"